reviews.review_text: I spent the night in Utah.. Nice sound..Good work Willy!! There are some really nice shows in December from 79'-81 and here is on of those! The FOTD is real nice Jerry gets it..the 1st set is packed with goodies and the China>Rider caps it off.. A snappy Scarlet>Fire to open> sets the pace for solid 2nd set..so please>GIVE IT A WHIRL>Forever Grateful>Forever Dead!!!!!!
they were fliping the tape poor whineing  boy
